text: Baiyangdian railway station () is a station Tianjin–Baoding intercity railway in Rongcheng County, Baoding, Hebei. == History == The station was opened on 28 December 2015, together with the Tianjin–Baoding intercity railway. == References == Category:Railway stations in Hebei Category:Stations on the Tianjin–Baoding Intercity Railway Category:Railway stations in China opened in 2015
title: Baiyangdian railway station
